{"version": "https://jsonfeed.org/version/1.1", "title": "\u57fa\u5ca9\u6587\u6863", "home_page_url": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/", "feed_url": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/feed_json_updated.json", "description": "Minecraft\u57fa\u5ca9\u7248\u5f00\u53d1\u6587\u6863", "icon": null, "authors": [], "language": "zh", "items": [{"id": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/blog/category/%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF/", "url": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/blog/category/%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF/", "title": "\u6280\u672f", "content_html": "<h1>\u6280\u672f</h1>", "image": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/blog/category/\u6280\u672f.png", "date_modified": "2026-05-24T07:17:07.350199+00:00", "date_published": "2026-05-24T07:17:07.350195+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/blog/archive/2024/", "url": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/blog/archive/2024/", "title": "2024", "content_html": "<h1>2024</h1>", "image": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/blog/archive/2024.png", "date_modified": "2026-05-24T07:17:07.315425+00:00", "date_published": "2026-05-24T07:17:07.315420+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/docs/client/levilamina-client/", "url": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/docs/client/levilamina-client/", "title": "LeviLamina\u5ba2\u6237\u7aef\u6a21\u7ec4", "content_html": "<h1>LeviLamina\u5ba2\u6237\u7aef\u6a21\u7ec4</h1>\n<p><strong>LeviLamina\u5ba2\u6237\u7aef\u6a21\u7ec4\uff08LeviLamina Client Mod\uff09</strong>\u662f\u57fa\u4e8eLeviLamina\u5ba2\u6237\u7aef\u6784\u5efa\u7684\u539f\u751f\u6269\u5c55\u5f62\u6001\u3002\u8be5\u5f62\u6001\u901a\u8fc7PreLoader\u5c06LeviLamina\u5ba2\u6237\u7aef\u6784\u5efa\u52a0\u8f7d\u5230\u53d7\u652f\u6301\u7684Windows\u7248Minecraft\u5ba2\u6237\u7aef\u8fdb\u7a0b\uff0c\u5e76\u7531LeviLami...</p>", "image": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/docs/client/levilamina-client.png", "date_modified": "2026-05-24T07:06:59+00:00", "date_published": "2026-05-24T05:44:16+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/docs/server/levilamina/", "url": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/docs/server/levilamina/", "title": "LeviLamina", "content_html": "<h1>LeviLamina</h1>\n<p><strong>LeviLamina</strong>\u662f\u9762\u5411Minecraft\u57fa\u5ca9\u7248\u7684\u7b2c\u4e09\u65b9\u6a21\u7ec4\u52a0\u8f7d\u5668\u3002\u5b83\u4ee5<strong>\u57fa\u5ca9\u7248\u4e13\u7528\u670d\u52a1\u5668\uff08Bedrock Dedicated Server\uff09</strong>\uff0c\u901a\u79f0BDS\uff0c\u4e3a\u4e3b\u8981\u8fd0\u884c\u57fa\u7840\uff0c\u901a\u8fc7\u9884\u52a0\u8f7d\u3001\u94a9\u5b50\u548c\u516c\u5171API\u4e3aC++\u6a21\u7ec4\u63d0\u4f9b\u547d\u4ee4\u3001\u4e8b\u4ef6\u3001\u8868\u5355\u3001\u670d\u52a1\u8bbf\u95ee\u3001\u914d\u7f6e\u3001\u6570\u636e\u5b58\u50a8\u3001\u65e5\u5fd7\u548c\u5e95\u5c42...</p>", "image": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/docs/server/levilamina.png", "date_modified": "2026-05-24T07:06:59+00:00", "date_published": "2026-05-23T15:16:46+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/guides/servers/levilamina/", "url": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/guides/servers/levilamina/", "title": "LeviLamina\u5165\u95e8", "content_html": "<h1>LeviLamina\u5165\u95e8</h1>\n<p>LeviLamina\u662f\u56f4\u7ed5BDS\u8fd0\u884c\u7684\u7b2c\u4e09\u65b9\u6a21\u7ec4\u52a0\u8f7d\u5668\u3002\u5b83\u4e0d\u662fBDS\u539f\u751f\u63d2\u4ef6\u7cfb\u7edf\uff1b\u4f60\u53ef\u4ee5\u628a\u5b83\u7406\u89e3\u6210\u4e00\u4e2a\u628aC++\u6a21\u7ec4\u63a5\u5165BDS\u6216\u53d7\u652f\u6301\u5ba2\u6237\u7aef\u7684\u8fd0\u884c\u65f6\u3002\u6982\u5ff5\u8bf4\u660e\u89c1<a href=\"../../docs/server/levilamina.md\">LeviLamina</a>\uff0cAPI\u6a21\u5757\u6982\u89c8\u89c1[LeviLam...</p>", "image": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/guides/servers/levilamina.png", "date_modified": "2026-05-24T07:06:59+00:00", "date_published": "2026-05-23T15:16:46+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/refs/server/bedrock-protocol-changelog/", "url": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/refs/server/bedrock-protocol-changelog/", "title": "\u57fa\u5ca9\u7248\u534f\u8bae\u53d8\u66f4\u7d22\u5f15", "content_html": "<h1>\u57fa\u5ca9\u7248\u534f\u8bae\u53d8\u66f4\u7d22\u5f15</h1>\n<p>\u672c\u6587\u7528\u4e8e\u6c47\u603b\u5b98\u65b9\u534f\u8bae\u4ed3\u5e93\u53d8\u66f4\u65e5\u5fd7\u6587\u4ef6\u7684\u7ed3\u6784\u4e0e\u4f7f\u7528\u65b9\u5f0f\uff0c\u4fbf\u4e8e\u5728\u7248\u672c\u8fc1\u79fb\u65f6\u5feb\u901f\u5b9a\u4f4d\u9ad8\u98ce\u9669\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u53d8\u5316\u3002</p>\n<h2>\u6765\u6e90</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\u6765\u6e90\u76ee\u5f55\uff1a<code>.knowledge\\\u57fa\u5ca9\u7248\u534f\u8bae\u5e93</code></li>\n<li>\u4e3b\u4ed3\u5e93\uff1a<a href=\"https://github.com/Mojang/bedrock-protocol-docs\">https://github.com/Mojang/bedrock-protocol-docs</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>...</h2>", "image": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/refs/server/bedrock-protocol-changelog.png", "date_modified": "2026-05-24T07:06:59+00:00", "date_published": "2026-05-24T06:55:41+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/refs/server/levilamina-api/", "url": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/refs/server/levilamina-api/", "title": "LeviLamina API\u6a21\u5757", "content_html": "<h1>LeviLamina API\u6a21\u5757</h1>\n<p>\u672c\u9875\u6982\u8ff0LeviLamina\u5b98\u65b9API\u53c2\u8003\u4e2d\u5217\u51fa\u7684\u4e3b\u8981\u6a21\u5757\u3002\u4e0b\u5217\u63a5\u53e3\u4ec5\u9002\u7528\u4e8eLeviLamina\u6a21\u7ec4\u5f00\u53d1\uff0c\u4e0d\u5c5e\u4e8eBDS\u539f\u751fAPI\u3002</p>\n<p>LeviLamina\u7684\u5b98\u65b9API\u6309<code>ll/api</code>\u7ec4\u7ec7\uff0c\u8986\u76d6\u57fa\u7840\u8bbe\u65bd\u3001\u6838\u5fc3\u7cfb\u7edf\u3001\u8f93\u5165\u8f93\u51fa\u3001\u5f02\u6b65\u4e0e\u7ebf\u7a0b\u3001\u6570\u636e\u4e0e\u5de5\u5177\u3001\u5e95\u5c42\u80fd\u529b\u548c\u4ec5\u5ba2\u6237\u7aef\u6a21\u5757\u3002\u76f8...</p>", "image": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/refs/server/levilamina-api.png", "date_modified": "2026-05-24T07:06:59+00:00", "date_published": "2026-05-23T15:16:46+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/translations/", "url": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/translations/", "title": "\u7ffb\u8bd1", "content_html": "<h1>\u7ffb\u8bd1</h1>\n<p>\u8fd9\u91cc\u81f4\u529b\u4e8e\u4e3a\u6240\u6709\u4f7f\u7528\u4e2d\u6587\u8bed\u8a00\u7684Minecraft\u57fa\u5ca9\u7248\u7814\u7a76\u8005\u63d0\u4f9b\u57fa\u5ca9\u7248\u5f00\u53d1\u76f8\u5173\u6587\u732e\u7684\u4e2d\u6587\u7ffb\u8bd1\u7248\u672c\u3002\u5982\u679c\u4f60\u662f\u4e00\u540dMinecraft\u57fa\u5ca9\u7248\u5f00\u53d1\u8005\uff0c\u6216\u8005\u5bf9Minecraft\u57fa\u5ca9\u7248\u5f00\u53d1\u611f\u5174\u8da3\uff0c\u4f60\u53ef\u4ee5\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\u5b66\u4e60\u5230\u6211\u4eec\u5df2\u7ffb\u8bd1\u7684\u5404\u7c7b\u6587\u732e\u4e2d\u7684\u76f8\u5173\u77e5\u8bc6\uff0c\u800c\u65e0\u9700\u5177\u5907\u82f1\u6587\u80fd\u529b\u3002\u5982\u679c\u4f60\u5bf9\u7ffb\u8bd1\u5de5\u4f5c\u611f\u5174\u8da3\uff0c\u4e5f\u6b22\u8fce\u4f60\u53c2\u4e0e\u5230\u6211\u4eec\u7684\u8fd9...</p>", "image": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/translations/index.png", "date_modified": "2026-05-24T07:06:59+00:00", "date_published": "2024-10-24T11:04:02+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/translations/levilamina/", "url": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/translations/levilamina/", "title": "LeviLamina\u6587\u6863\u5f52\u6863", "content_html": "<h1>LeviLamina\u6587\u6863\u5f52\u6863</h1>\n<p>\u672c\u9875\u6536\u5f55<code>.knowledge\\LeviLamina\u6e90\u7801\u53ca\u6587\u6863\\</code>\u4e2d\u7684LeviLamina\u5b98\u65b9\u8d44\u6599\u8109\u7edc\uff0c\u7528\u4e8e\u8bf4\u660e\u8fd9\u4e9b\u5185\u5bb9\u5728\u672c\u7ad9\u7684\u843d\u4f4d\u65b9\u5f0f\u3002</p>\n<h2>\u5904\u7406\u7b56\u7565</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>\u6982\u5ff5\u4e0e\u603b\u89c8</strong>\uff1a\u5df2\u5e76\u5165[LeviLamina](../../docs/server/levilamina.md...</li>\n</ul>", "image": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/translations/levilamina/index.png", "date_modified": "2026-05-24T07:06:59+00:00", "date_published": "2026-05-24T07:06:59+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/translations/levilamina/architecture/", "url": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/translations/levilamina/architecture/", "title": "\u9879\u76ee\u67b6\u6784", "content_html": "<h1>\u9879\u76ee\u67b6\u6784</h1>\n<h2>\u76ee\u5f55\u7ed3\u6784</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><code>src/</code>\uff1a\u901a\u7528\u4e0e\u670d\u52a1\u7aef\u4ee3\u7801\u3002</li>\n<li><code>src-client/</code>\uff1a\u5ba2\u6237\u7aef\u4e13\u7528\u4ee3\u7801\u3002</li>\n<li><code>src-server/</code>\uff1a\u670d\u52a1\u7aef\u4e13\u7528\u4ee3\u7801\u3002</li>\n<li><code>src-test/</code>\uff1a\u6d4b\u8bd5\u4ee3\u7801\u3002</li>\n<li><code>docs/</code>\uff1a\u6587\u6863\u3002</li>\n<li><code>scripts/</code>\uff1a\u6784\u5efa\u4e0e\u5de5\u5177\u811a\u672c\u3002</li>\n<li><code>builder/</code>\uff1a\u5934\u6587...</li>\n</ul>", "image": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/assets/images/social/translations/levilamina/architecture.png", "date_modified": "2026-05-24T07:06:59+00:00", "date_published": "2026-05-24T07:06:59+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/translations/levilamina/build-guide/", "url": "https://miemiemethod.github.io/bedrock-docs/translations/levilamina/build-guide/", "title": "\u6784\u5efa\u6307\u5357", "content_html": "<h1>\u6784\u5efa\u6307\u5357</h1>\n<h2>\u524d\u